Aragorn, Heir to the White City x 3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(11)">Ranger&#39;s Sword</a><br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(301)">Aragorn&#39;s Bow</a><br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(306)">Boromir, Lord of Gondor</a> x 3<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(305)">Blade of Gondor</a><br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(937)">Flaming Brand</a> x 2<br>
<a href="javascript:card_browser(303)">Armor</a> x 2<br>
